{
  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Fix axios CVE-2026-42035: upgrade to 1.15.1+ via npm override (#10821)\n\naxios 1.15.0 (transitive via wait-on) is vulnerable to arbitrary HTTP\nheader injection via prototype pollution (CVE-2026-42035). Add npm\noverride to force axios ^1.15.1 (resolves to 1.15.2).\n\nDiscovered via CNCF Insights scan of peer project kiali/kiali#9611.\n\nSigned-off-by: Copilot <copilot@github.com>\nCo-authored-by: Copilot <copilot@github.com>\nCo-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>",
